<?php include_once($_SERVER['DOCUMENT_ROOT'] . '/assets/php/html/min/imports/importPath.php'); ?><!doctypehtml><html lang=en><meta charset=utf-8><?php include_once('global/sharedStyles.php'); ?><link href=/assets/styles/css/min/local/help/how-to-redeem/instructions.min.css rel=stylesheet><title>How to Redeem: Borderlands: TPS - ShiftCodesTK</title><meta content="How to Redeem: TPS - ShiftCodesTK"name=title><meta content="How to Redeem: Borderlands: TPS - ShiftCodesTK"property=og:title><meta content="How to Redeem: Borderlands: TPS - ShiftCodesTK"property=twitter:title><meta content="How to redeem SHiFT Codes in Borderlands: The Pre-Sequel"name=description><meta content="How to redeem SHiFT Codes in Borderlands: The Pre-Sequel"property=og:description><meta content="How to redeem SHiFT Codes in Borderlands: The Pre-Sequel"property=twitter:description><meta name=canonical href=https://shiftcodestk.com/help/how-to-redeem/tps><meta content=https://shiftcodestk.com/help/how-to-redeem/tps property=og:url><meta content=tps_6 name=header:image><meta content=https://shiftcodestk.com/assets/img/metadata/tps/6.png property=og:image><meta content=https://shiftcodestk.com/assets/img/metadata/tps/6.png property=twitter:image><link href=/assets/manifests/tps.webmanifest rel=manifest><meta content=#1e90ff name=theme-color-tm id=theme_color_tm><?php include_once('global/head.php'); ?><body data-theme=tps><?php include_once('global/beforeContent.php'); ?><?php include_once('global/main-header.php'); ?><main class=content-wrapper><?php include_once('local/how-to-redeem-instructions.php'); ?></main><div class=setup><div class="step 1">Navigate to the Main Menu. Then, select <em>Extras</em>.</div><div class="step 2">Select <em>SHiFT Code</em>.</div><div class="step 3">If you have not accepted the latest SHiFT <em>Terms of Service</em> and <em>Privacy Policy</em>, you will be prompted to do so.</div><div class="step 4">If you have not already registered and signed in to <strong>SHiFT</strong>, you will be prompted to do so.</div><div class="step 5">Once you have reached the <strong>My Rewards</strong> page, press the indicated key to reach the <strong>SHiFT Code</strong> page.</div><div class="step 6">Enter the 25-character SHiFT Code into the provided fields. Once you are finished, click <em>Submit</em>.</div><div class="step 7">If successful, you will receive a confirmation message. The reward from the SHiFT Code will also appear on the <strong>My Rewards</strong> page.</div><div class="step 8">Next, make your way to <strong>Concordia</strong>. Once you have arrived, find the <strong>SHiFT Vending Machine</strong>. It is located near the <strong>elevator to The Meriff's Office</strong>.</div><div class="step 9">Interact with the machine. Then, switch to the <strong>Repository</strong> tab.</div><div class="step 10">Select your rewards to claim them. You can now also enter more SHiFT Codes in the fields provided on the right side of the menu.</div><div class="step 11">You can now make your way to the <strong>Golden Chest</strong> in <strong>Concordia</strong> to spend your Golden Keys. The Golden Chest is located near the <strong>vendors</strong> and <strong>Quick Change station</strong>. Opening the chest will cost <strong>one Golden Key</strong>, and the rewards will be droppped at the <strong>level of your current character</strong>, regardless of playthrough.</div></div><?php include_once('local/support-footer.php'); ?><?php include_once('global/afterContent.php'); ?><?php include_once('global/sharedScripts.php'); ?><script async src="/assets/scripts/min/local/help/how-to-redeem/instructions.min.js?v=<?php echo $svQueryString; ?>"></script>